  "QuestText": {
    "QuestInfo": [
      {
        "Language": "JPN",
        "Name": "\u3042\u308B\u591C\u30D5\u30EB\u30D5\u30EB\u3092\u72E9\u308B",
        "Client": "\u6ED1\u820C\u306E\u826F\u3044\u7537\u6027",
        "Description": "\u5BD2\u3055\u306B\u30D6\u30EB\u30D6\u30EB\u9707\u3048\u3066\u591C\u91E3\u308A\u3092\r\n\u3057\u3066\u3044\u305F\u3089\u6025\u306B\u30D7\u30EB\u30D7\u30EB\u3057\u305F\u584A\u2026\r\n\u305D\u3046\u3001\u30D5\u30EB\u30D5\u30EB\u304C\u964D\u3063\u3066\u6765\u305F\uFF01\r\n\u30CC\u30EB\u30CC\u30EB\u306E\u53E3\u306B\u98DF\u308F\u308C\u308B\u524D\u306B\u3001\r\n\u6C37\u4E0A\u3092\u30C4\u30EB\u30C4\u30EB\u6ED1\u3063\u3066\u9003\u3052\u305F\u3088\u3002\r\n\u653E\u3063\u3066\u304A\u3051\u3070\u3001\u307F\u308B\u307F\u308B\u3046\u3061\u306B\r\n\u88AB\u5BB3\u304C\u5E83\u307E\u308B\u3002\u72E9\u731F\u3092\u983C\u3093\u3060\u305C\u3002",
        "Target": "\u30D5\u30EB\u30D5\u30EB\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Night of the Khezu",
        "Client": "Poetically Spoken Man",
        "Description": "I was out fishing; everything dark\r\nand gloomy. When suddenly down\r\nflew a Khezu; slimy and gooey.\r\nHorrified to find there were no eyes\r\nthat would twinkle, only a blubbery\r\nneck...veiny and wrinkled.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Khezu",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "La nuit du Khezu",
        "Client": "Homme po\u00E9tique",
        "Description": "Je p\u00EAchais tranquillement dans\r\nla nuit, quand un Khezu est arriv\u00E9,\r\nplein de gadoue. Je ne voyais pas\r\nces yeux, j\u0027\u00E9tais horrifi\u00E9.\r\nFace \u00E0 moi ne se tenait qu\u0027une\r\nnuque \u00E9paisse, turgescente et rid\u00E9e.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Khezu",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "La notte del Khezu",
        "Client": "Uomo poetico",
        "Description": "Ero fuori a pescare, tutto era\r\nbuio intorno. Ma dal nulla \u00E8\r\napparso un Khezu viscido e\r\nmelmoso. Non aveva gli occhi,\r\ndavvero terrificante, ma il\r\nsuo collo era enorme, venoso\r\ne rugoso.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Khezu",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Die Nacht des Khezu",
        "Client": "Verhinderter Poet",
        "Description": "Ich war angeln in dunkler Nacht,\r\nda flog ein Khezu her in klebrig-\r\nschleimiger Pracht.\r\nKeine Augen sah ich funkeln,\r\nnur ein aufgeschwollener Hals...\r\n\u00FCbers\u00E4t mit Adern und Runzeln.",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Khezu.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "La noche del Khezu",
        "Client": "Hombre de rico vocabulario",
        "Description": "Pescaba yo al ocaso lento y\r\noscuro, cuando presto vol\u00F3 un\r\nKhezu sobre el r\u00EDo. Hui raudo\r\npara evitar el apuro, pues en\r\nsu mirada sent\u00ED un designio\r\nsombr\u00EDo. \u00A1Ve por \u00E9l y dale\r\nduro, da con br\u00EDo!",
        "Target": "Caza un Khezu",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041D\u043E\u0447\u044C \u041A\u0435\u0437\u0443",
        "Client": "\u041F\u043E\u044D\u0442",
        "Description": "\u042F \u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u043B \u0440\u044B\u0431\u0430\u0447\u0438\u0442\u044C, \u0431\u044B\u043B\u043E \u0442\u0435\u043C\u043D\u043E\r\n\u0438 \u043C\u0440\u0430\u0447\u043D\u043E. \u0412\u043D\u0435\u0437\u0430\u043F\u043D\u043E \u0432\u043D\u0438\u0437 \u0441\u043B\u0435\u0442\u0435\u043B\r\n\u041A\u0435\u0437\u0443, \u0441\u043A\u043E\u043B\u044C\u0437\u043A\u0438\u0439 \u0438 \u043B\u0438\u043F\u043A\u0438\u0439.\r\n\u042F \u0434\u0430\u0436\u0435 \u0433\u043B\u0430\u0437 \u0443 \u043D\u0435\u0433\u043E \u043D\u0435 \u0432\u0438\u0434\u0435\u043B,\r\n\u0442\u043E\u043B\u044C\u043A\u043E \u043C\u043E\u0440\u0449\u0438\u043D\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0443\u044E \u0448\u0435\u044E\r\n\u0441 \u0443\u0437\u0435\u043B\u043A\u0430\u043C\u0438 \u0432\u0435\u043D. \u0423\u0436\u0430\u0441!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u041A\u0435\u0437\u0443",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Noc Khezu",
        "Client": "Poetycki m\u0119\u017Cczyzna",
        "Description": "By\u0142em na rybach \u2013 mroczno,\r\nponuro. Nagle leci Khezu,\r\njakby \u015Bluzu chmura. Straszny\r\nwidok, nie ma to-to oczu,\r\ntylko gruba szyja z z\u0119bami\r\nna ko\u0144cu...",
        "Target": "Upoluj Khezu",
        "Fail": "Nagroda = 0 lub koniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "Noite do Khezu",
        "Client": "Homem falando poeticamente",
        "Description": "L\u00E1 estava eu, pescando em paz,\r\nnum breu que s\u00F3 a noite traz.\r\nDo c\u00E9u, veio um Khezu limoso.\r\nDizem que escapar fedendo\r\n\u00E9 melhor que morrer cheiroso.\r\nFugi apavorado de terr\u00EDvel fim.\r\nTu podes ca\u00E7\u00E1-lo por mim, sim?",
        "Target": "Cace um Khezu",
        "Fail": "A recompensa chega a 0\r\nou o tempo expira"
      },
      {
        "Language": "KOR",
        "Name": "\uC5B4\uB290 \uBC24 \uD478\uB8E8\uD478\uB8E8\uB97C \uC0AC\uB0E5\uD55C\uB2E4",
